text: Violeta Ivanova Zareva (; born 29 May 1968) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Sofia
